      <title>泰国领导人公布重新获得旅游热点头衔和电动汽车投资的路线图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/thai-leader-unveils-roadmap-to-regain-tourism-hotspot-title-ev-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 公布了一份路线图，旨在将该国发展成为旅游、健康和电动汽车生产的区域中心，同时他力图吸引急需的外国投资，以启动背负高额家庭债务和通货紧缩的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/thai-leader-unveils-roadmap-to-regain-tourism-hotspot-title-ev-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 03:36:02 GMT</pubDate>
